item.title: CVE-2021-20726|2024-08-03T17:53:21.826Z -- overwolf%20ltd. -- the%20installer%20of%20overwolf
item.description: Untrusted search path vulnerability in The Installer of Overwolf 2.168.0.n and earlier allows an attacker to gain privileges and execute arbitrary code with the privilege of the user invoking the installer via a Trojan horse DLL in an unspecified directory.
